snippet.title: Warranty Man // Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/3262570/Warranty_Man/

First person scary game set in an underground parking garage. Find your lost parking card, collect some cash to pay for your parking and get out before Warranty Man finds you and sells you auto insurance.

Developed by
ENT3RWH
